Package: anneal
Title: Optimizers for the Anvil Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sebastian", "Fischer", , "seb.fischer@tutamail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9609-3197"))
  )
Description: Functional optimizers for use with the anvil code transformation
    framework. Provides optimizer abstractions and implementations (SGD, etc.)
    that work with immutable array state.
